c=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有愛就訂 考慮緊嘅就睇多幾次套戲 唔係唔訂下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :點樣可以保養隻HOT TOYS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 以下轉自網上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要被太陽長時間直射<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n合金長時間在太陽下爆曬，高溫會導致顏色變淺，表面油漆可能會起泡及龜烈，嚴重影響figures的外觀。要留意，就算放到飾櫃但長時間用射燈照視，都可能會導致上述問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n避免在雙手不乾淨時觸碰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手上的汗水與油份很容易黏在合金表面，久而久之就會氧化成一層白白的薄膜，所以接觸figures前最好先將雙手清潔乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意溫度及濕度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港天氣潮濕，所以要十分留意家中的濕度，因為太潮濕會引致生銹;至於溫度方面，太大的溫差會導致熱漲冷縮，令hot toys變得脆弱。所以將空間保持乾爽對保存hot Toys很重要。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放入玻璃櫃display , 得閒用除塵帚 掃幾下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIM電池保養方法：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nim果d版電仔唔好長時間放係本體入面<br />\n玩完 着完燈 j完好拎哂d電出黎<br />\n因為d版電仔放係本體入面耐左會發漲<br />\n最後會爆漿 會損壞im d電路<br />\n大家玩im開心之餘記得留意下電池咩情況 （BY 舒洛特 巴打）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n======================================================================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒圖時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/153636_2c97051286580b742a428f816691b07a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F153636_2c97051286580b742a428f816691b07a.png&h=1acebab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/153640_c09924e055337313a83f1ea689440879.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F153640_c09924e055337313a83f1ea689440879.png&h=f3ddd0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/153646_0ecdc29b1419f3b8027e71d31edd3c51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F153646_0ecdc29b1419f3b8027e71d31edd3c51.jpg&h=5efe3aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/153648_e24a94514e57fbbe3428e6d3ac53008f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F153648_e24a94514e57fbbe3428e6d3ac53008f.jpg&h=1ea6614c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/153651_43bf44fae9abc0450fa486ecccdbeaba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F153651_43bf44fae9abc0450fa486ecccdbeaba.jpg&h=7514ca8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n======================================================================<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e195f219fad364ca8c3fe2d9b3decfdc8d6ac265","tid":890534,"uid":193775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:42:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"83d239aabae039bf8375ecbac37be25fedf5e2b3","tid":890534,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:17:49.000Z","msg":"咁快開新post"}]}